# Skill: UI Redesign - VNPT Business Management

## Muc dich
Skill nay la wrapper trung lap, model-agnostic cho workflow redesign UI trong he thong VNPT Business Management.

No duoc thiet ke de dung duoc voi:
- Claude
- Codex
- Cursor
- ChatGPT
- Gemini
- bat ky AI assistant nao co the doc file trong repo

## Dau vao ho tro
- Full URL, vi du `http://127.0.0.1:5174/contracts`
- Path, vi du `/contracts`
- Route name, vi du `contracts`
- Tab key, vi du `contract_list`
- Mo ta component, vi du `modals` hoac `fee-collection modals`

## Nguon huong dan chuan
- `docs/ui-redesign.md`

AI model phai doc file nay truoc khi sua code.

## Workflow 5 Buoc

### Buoc 1: Xac dinh target
- Parse input thanh route, tab key, hoac component description
- Map target thanh file React/TypeScript can sua

### Buoc 2: Doc va phan tich
- Doc file component lien quan
- So sanh voi design system trong `docs/ui-redesign.md`
- Lap delta checklist truoc khi sua

### Buoc 3: Sua dung pham vi
- Chi sua JSX `return (...)` va file-level style constants
- Khong sua logic, hooks, state, types, imports, handlers, API calls

### Buoc 4: Validate
- Chay `cd frontend && npm run lint`
- Neu co loi TypeScript, sua den khi pass hoac bao cao ro blocker

### Buoc 5: Bao cao
- Liet ke file da sua
- Liet ke cac thay doi chinh theo before -> after
- Bao cao ket qua lint

## Rang buoc bat buoc
- Dung design tokens cua project
- Dung `material-symbols-outlined`, khong dung `lucide-react`
- Giu nguyen business logic
- Uu tien giam whitespace du thua va compact layout

## Tham chieu
- `docs/ui-redesign.md`
- `.claude/skills/ui-redesign/SKILL.md`
- `frontend/tailwind.config.js`
